{"id": 2447, "genre": 1000, "title": "假如没有智能手机，你觉得多长时间算得上“长”？", "description": "换句话说，你在没有其他事情要忙、又没有手机的情况下，可以坚持过多久？（题图来自：iStock © Triangle_c）", "record_count": 7368, "comment_count": 65, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180703100416P2tHiCrYGDlOzSmx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-03T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4441, "title": "假如没有智能手机，你觉得多长时间算得上“长”？", "content": "假如没有智能手机，你觉得多长时间算很长？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 290368, "content": "开什么玩笑，一秒钟都不行", "image": "img/option/option/20180703120324bJ1sPYV5Nk2DAyEZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290369, "content": "立刻马上就要摸手机，也就能撑个五秒十秒吧", "image": "img/option/option/20180703120407zlk8q5QR2sjg6SpX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290376, "content": "过个两三分钟、三五分钟，能量条就逐渐降到最低点了", "image": "img/option/option/201807031219284P6IGs5mKugS1ecr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290377, "content": "发发呆，过个十几二十分钟没问题", "image": "img/option/option/20180703120446P1ScHDNGVfjBai2F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290379, "content": "一个小时感觉刚刚好，能过得去", "image": "img/option/option/20180703123611dGqETlFvr6zXibm2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290380, "content": "三四个小时没问题，大不了摸本书看", "image": "img/option/option/20180703121328luX3UzO7NK0m1L6x.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290381, "content": "一天都不要紧，就算不工作不娱乐也有好多事做", "image": "img/option/option/20180703123946I4m8HNY0p9fukUnF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290382, "content": "两三天没问题，经常手机扔角落里也想不起来", "image": "img/option/option/20180703124122rT62Lab3POul5YFn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290383, "content": "还好吧？一个礼拜才好意思说是“一长段时间”", "image": "img/option/option/20180703124845FRj07dQvoZ45yIVc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290384, "content": "再长也可以，平时也只有非看不可的时候才拿出手机", "image": "img/option/option/20180703122833b9CuOTRpB5qlzWkc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}